CXR1218.Texto: Lungs are clear bilaterally with no focal infiltrate, pleural effusion, or pneumothoraces. Cardiomediastinal silhouette is within normal limits. No acute bony or soft tissue abnormality.

Utterance.PhraseText: No acute bony or soft tissue abnormality.
Cardiomediastinal silhouette is within normal limits.
Lungs are clear bilaterally with no focal infiltrate, pleural effusion, or pneumothoraces.
